headline: Scotiabank Keeps Sector Perform Rating on EQT After Q3 Results
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) is one of the 15 Best Aggressive Growth Stocks to Buy Right Now. On October 22, Scotiabank reiterated its Sector Perform rating on EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) with a price target of $70. This decision came after the company reported results for the third quarter of 2025. EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) shared impressive figures […]
